The user should inherit a class from the defagenthandler:

The user should override the following function:
update(simtime): this function should contain the update code for the agent type.

The following functions are provided by the agenthandler:

sendMessage(totype, toid, message): the agent can send the message 'message' to the agent of type 'to_type' and  id 'to_id' 
getMessages(): this function will return a list of all messages. Each message is a list of fromType, fromId, simtime and the actual message
readState(): this function will return a dictionary of the current state of the agent
writeState(): this function will update the dictionary defined by self.fields to the database

kill(): this function kills the agents.
